### SkillBridge API — happy-path walkthrough
### Use with the VS Code "REST Client" extension. Run requests top to bottom.
### Named requests (# @name ...) let later requests reuse values automatically.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### 0. Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 1. Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Ritik", "email": "ritik@example.com", "password": "secret123" }

### 2. Login (token is auto-captured for the requests below)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "ritik@example.com", "password": "secret123" }

### 3. Who am I
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Ingest a GitHub profile
# @name ingestGithub
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ingest/github
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "username": "octocat" }

### 5. Poll that source until status = processed (needs a working Gemini key)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sources/{{ingestGithub.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. List all sources
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sources
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Build the Current State from processed sources
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profile/build
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Read the profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Benchmark: level vs experience
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/benchmark
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "experienceYears": 2, "targetRole": "Senior Full Stack Engineer" }

### 10. Gap analysis + learning plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/analysis
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "targetRole": "Senior Full Stack Engineer" }

### 11. Generate gap-closing projects
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/projects/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. List generated projects
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. Interview readiness
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/interview/readiness
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "targetRole": "Senior Backend Engineer" }

### 14. Job match against a pasted JD
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/jobmatch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "jdText": "We are hiring a Senior Backend Engineer with Node.js, TypeScript, MongoDB and AWS to build scalable APIs and mentor the team." }

### 15. Market worth (rough, low-confidence)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/worth
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "experienceYears": 2, "location": "Bangalore, India", "targetRole": "Senior Engineer" }

### 16. Career plan (job-search + income ideas)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/career/plan
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "targetRole": "Senior Full Stack Engineer" }
